2013-08-14 Anton Kolesov   <akolesov@synopsys.com>

	* build-all.sh: Unset some environment variables for example CROSS_COMPILE
	and ARCH. Tools makefiles recognize these variable and might use them in
	an undesirable way. For example CROSS_COMPILE has a predence over
	toolchain we are building and this for example might cause a big endian
	toolchain to have little endian standard libraries.

